                    "body": "Eventually we need to implement the ability to write an Arrow IPC stream to disk while reading a Parquet file (or any dataset source):\r\n\r\n* Read a RecordBatch/Table from the file in one thread\r\n* Write to IPC stream/file on disk in another thread\r\n\r\nOnce the read is completed we can memory map the IPC file so the memory use will stay low",
